channel.title: Weird problems
channel.description: Ok when i run my script it goes perfectly until it gets to one point. Now what it does here is maaad weird, the mouse is still, but a flag suddenly appears on the MM and clicks the game tab about 5 times even though its open (and i know this because i see the mouse moving a bit on the game tab), and then it lags forever. After it walks to the flag taht appeard on the MM it lags more, waits, and then starts the procedure it was orignally supposed to do int he first place. But then towards the begining of this procedure it lags more and it goes sooo slow. Like, it takes forever to do one thing i coded. This is the ONLY TIME something like this happened with this script because it was working perfectly the other day, and then last night this shit started... Can it be my computer? beacuse when i looked at the bugged procedures there is NOTHING i can find wrong at all.. no waits, anything..not even anything wrong in the main loop.
